I'm not good at cooking, actually.

00:16:35.432 --> 00:16:37.518
I'm good at eating, though.

00:16:50.864 --> 00:16:54.368
You eat like you really enjoy the food.

00:16:59.498 --> 00:17:00.332
‎Again?

00:17:01.208 --> 00:17:04.878
No, um… This is because…

00:17:06.088 --> 00:17:07.506
