It looks similar, though…

00:19:14.216 --> 00:19:17.219
JANG-JORIM

00:20:08.645 --> 00:20:09.855
Amazing…

00:20:10.897 --> 00:20:13.025
Truly a genius. A genius.

00:20:17.904 --> 00:20:19.072
I'm so jealous.

