If I had this kind of talent,
I bet I would have no worries.

00:20:29.458 --> 00:20:32.878
I see… Your mother is pretty mad, huh?

00:20:34.546 --> 00:20:39.092
I know. It's my fault.

00:20:39.718 --> 00:20:41.636
But when you're here, don't you sometimes

00:20:42.220 --> 00:20:45.140
feel like you've become so stupid?

00:20:46.641 --> 00:20:48.852
Things like checking the mail,

00:20:48.935 --> 00:20:51.063
and riding the bus…

00:20:51.146 --> 00:20:54.941
Things that I used to do normally
have suddenly become so difficult.

00:20:56.151 --> 00:20:59.112
‎If someone were to say,

00:20:59.196 --> 00:21:02.324
‎"That's the life you chose,"

00:21:03.116 --> 00:21:04.993
I'd have nothing to say back.

00:21:05.911 --> 00:21:06.787
But…

00:21:08.246 --> 00:21:09.915
I used to be a little more competent.

00:21:12.417 --> 00:21:13.668
What are you saying?

00:21:15.253 --> 00:21:16.213
Rin,

00:21:16.713 --> 00:21:18.465
you're very competent.

00:21:19.049 --> 00:21:20.550
You'll get through this soon.

00:21:20.634 --> 00:21:23.095
Trust me on this one.

00:21:24.679 --> 00:21:25.806
Okay?

00:21:27.015 --> 00:21:29.351
Okay. Thank you.

00:21:31.144 --> 00:21:34.231
I only have a year left,
so I'll try my best.

00:21:36.358 --> 00:21:38.735
Okay. You can talk to me anytime.

00:21:43.448 --> 00:21:45.242
You need to go back soon, right?

00:21:46.159 --> 00:21:47.494
What will you do for lunch?

00:21:48.578 --> 00:21:51.790
I'll just grab some onigiri.

