-Input?
-Yes.

00:23:14.080 --> 00:23:18.251
I'm thinking of doing a Korean-style dish
for our new menu item,

00:23:18.335 --> 00:23:19.502
but…

00:23:21.087 --> 00:23:23.048
it's not going so well.

00:23:23.131 --> 00:23:24.466
I'd appreciate your advice.

00:23:26.593 --> 00:23:27.677
Of course.

00:23:30.555 --> 00:23:33.183
Before that, may I ask you one thing?

00:23:33.850 --> 00:23:34.768
Yes?

00:23:35.894 --> 00:23:38.146
My name is Park Rin.

00:23:38.855 --> 00:23:39.814
What is your name?

00:23:42.275 --> 00:23:43.818
I'm Hase Taiga.

00:23:45.362 --> 00:23:47.530
I'll call you Taiga then.

00:23:53.620 --> 00:23:57.290
I want to use okra for its unique texture.

00:23:58.458 --> 00:24:00.460
It's my first time seeing

00:24:00.543 --> 00:24:01.795
-an okra.
-Huh?

